Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:18.93,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Railgun!
Dialogue: 2,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.39,Note,Maf,0,0,0,,Đao Đóa Dã = Rèn đúc kiếm
